.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Logging utilities and logger class for engine diagnostics\&. 

Provides a flexible logging system with multiple severity levels (Trace, Debug, Info, Warn, Error, Critical)\&. Supports logging to console and optional file output\&. Designed for easy integration into the engine for runtime diagnostics, debugging, and error reporting\&.

.PP
Features:
.IP "\(bu" 2
Stream-style logging with operator<< overloads
.IP "\(bu" 2
Configurable log levels to filter messages
.IP "\(bu" 2
Optional file logging with append/overwrite modes
.PP

.PP
Usage: 
.PP
.nf
ENGINE_INFO << "Engine started successfully\&.";
ENGINE_WARN << "Low memory warning\&.";
ENGINE_ERROR << "Failed to load texture: " << texturePath;

.fi
.PP
 
